  <brief_title>Study of Two Techniques of Rectal Reservoir in Low Anterior Resection of Rectum</brief_title>
  <official_title>Prospective Randomized Study of Two Techniques of Rectal Reservoir in Low Anterior Resection of Rectum</official_title>
  <sponsors>
